               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240218-146-cd806" type="crimeDate">23d of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-146-off805 t18240218-146-cd806"></join>, a coat, value 50 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240218-146-victim1378" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Thurling
                        <interp inst="t18240218-146-victim1378" type="surname" value="Thurling"></interp>
